<HEADLINE>
INTERNET SURFING HARMS YOUR SOCIAL LIFE  
 
</HEADLINE>
  
 (ATTN: Commentary Editors)   (This 350-word ``separate-buy'' article is from THE INDEPENDENT
newspaper in London.)  
  
