<P>
   FOOD-BACONSOUP _ DAYTON, Ohio _ I remember the summer day in
1996 when I first tasted Nueske's applewood smoked bacon on a
state-of-the-art BLT. Nearly four years later, delivery to
supermarkets remains irregular even when the butcher begs suppliers
for it. Fortunately, Nueske's now has a mail-order catalog and a
Web site. With recipe for bacon soup. (Heller, Dayton Daily News)
MOVED
</P>
