   COXNET-WRESTLING PAGE
</P>
<P>
   EDs: The weekly CoxNet wrestling page is available Wednesdays by
3 p.m. EST. Keying to the Monday wrestling events, It's good for
publication any day through Sunday. Here are the elements on the
page, which are also moving on the entertainment wire:
</P>
<P>
   WRESTLING-SHOW _ ATLANTA _ It's 15 minutes before a live taping
of the World Wrestling Federation's ``Raw is War'' event in Atlanta
and the faithful can hardly handle the wait. ``I'm ready to rock,''
said fan Mickey Davies. ``I want to see my boys. Whoooohooooo!''
Davies, 19, is not the only one fidgeting in his seat. The crowd of
28,000 is waiting to go nuts. They want to crank it up. They know
what's coming. The house lights go down. The Dome erupts. It's so
loud you can't hear the person yelling next to you. Handmade signs
of all different shapes and colors are hoisted in the air as if
they were flags raised in battle. It's show time. (Duncan, Cox News
Service) WITH PHOTOS
</P>
<P>
   WRESTLING-GRAPEVINE _ News, notes and gossip from the werstling
industry. (Allen, Cox News Service).
</P>
