<DOCTYPE> NEWS STORY </DOCTYPE>
<DATE_TIME> 2000-03-01 14:14 </DATE_TIME>
<HEADER>
A3238 &Cx1f; tad-z
u v BC-SPOT-BJT02-COX     03-01 1437
