   STUDENT-MUSIC (Undated) _ Top-rank contemporary composers who
write pieces for intermediate musicians. By Anthony Tommasini.
</P>
<P>
   COOPER-NOVEL (New York) _ A symposium on the provocative novels
of Dennis Cooper. By Kathryn Shattuck.
</P>
<P>
   BOOK-TALK (Undated) _ The weekly books column. By Martin Arnold.
</P>
<P>
   OLY-SYDNEY (Sydney, Austrialia) _ Arts Abroad: Sydney is awash
in pre-Olympics cultural festivals. By John Shaw.
</P>
<P>
   STRIKES-FILM-REVIEW (Undated) _ ``Three Strikes'': D.J. Pooh,
