</P>
<P>
   ARATON-COLUMN (Paterson, N.J.) _ Sports of The Times column on
athletics and education, told through the story of a teacher of
gifted children at a Patterson High School. Jane Silverstein's
students know what it means to really work for an education, and
the real value of one when they get it. By Harvey Araton.
</P>
