   BBO-BRAVES-ROCKER (New York) _ A ruling by the arbitrator on the
length of John Rocker's suspension is due today. By Murray Chass.
</P>
<P>
   AMERICAS-CUP (Auckland, New Zealand) _ Race 5, weather
permitting, in the finals of the America's Cup, with New Zealand,
the defending champion, leading Prada of Italy, 4-0, in the
best-five-out-of-nine series. By Herb McCormick.
</P>
