<P>
   AETNA-WLP (Thousand Oaks, Calif.) _ Aetna said Wednesday that
Wellpoint Health Networks and ING America Insurance Holdings have
expressed interest in buying the company for about $10 billion. As
currently structured, Aetna shareholders would get $44 in cash and
$26 in stock. By Chris Sieroty.
</P>
