be released today. The story has been the same for the past three
years and now, thanks to a dot-com companies, television has gotten
even more commercial-dense. By Marla Matzer Rose.
</P>
<P>
   INSURE-CONNELL (Los Angeles) _ State Controller Kathleen Connell
