</P>
<P>
   BBN-ROCKER (Orlando, Fla.) _ Atlanta Braves relief pitcher John
Rocker's suspension is reduced to two weeks and he can join his
team in spring training as early as Friday. By Larry Whiteside. 800
words.
</P>
<P>
   &UR; The Boston Globe &LR;  &QC;
