<DOCTYPE> NEWS STORY </DOCTYPE>
<DATE_TIME> 2000-03-01 19:49 </DATE_TIME>
<HEADER>
A3688 &Cx1f; tad-z
u f BC-DOW02-COX     03-01 0775
