<DOCTYPE> NEWS STORY </DOCTYPE>
<DATE_TIME> 2000-03-01 21:06 </DATE_TIME>
<HEADER>
A3779 &Cx1f; ttj-z
u w BC-STATE-DRUGS-HNS &LR;      03-01 0742
