<DOCNO> NYT20000301.0483 </DOCNO>
<DOCTYPE> NEWS STORY </DOCTYPE>
<DATE_TIME> 2000-03-01 22:07 </DATE_TIME>
<HEADER>
A3875 &Cx1f; tab-z
r k BC-TOOEASY-EXECUTIONS-US     03-01 1177
</HEADER>
<BODY>
<SLUG> BC-TOOEASY-EXECUTIONS-US-RESEND-INDEPENDENT-NYTSF </SLUG>
<HEADLINE>
USA: WHERE JUSTICE IS TAINTED BY A LETHAL CYNICISM  
 
</HEADLINE>
  
